  john --format=raw-md5 --wordlist=/usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt hash.txt

  ⚠️ Ako wordlist ne postoji, možda trebaš ga prvo raspakirati:
  gunzip /usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt.gz
